PREAMBLE

This License governs the use of an e-commerce marketplace backend system
(hereinafter "Backend Software" or "Software"). The Backend Software includes
but is not limited to: REST/GraphQL APIs, server-side business logic, database
schema and migrations, authentication/authorization systems, payment processing,
inventory management, vendor management, order processing pipelines, admin
dashboards, and all server-side infrastructure code.

The Licensor retains all intellectual property rights in the Software. This
License imposes mandatory attribution requirements for API documentation,
source code, environment configurations, and deployment artifacts. These
conditions are binding, non-waivable, and apply whether the Software is
deployed internally, to staging, or to production.

